column5: Hey guys check this out... the first one of the season!!  Thanks to Northamfishing and Kesagami Lodge  Click here to view!!
Thats a great video clip TJ ..  ..too bad that pike wasnt on my spinnerbait  lol...lol
That was awesome TJ.  Thanks!  Corn Nug
Now that is fun to watch!
Thanks TJ, Northamfishing and Kesagami Lodge!!  Love these videos!  Probably a good thing I don't own an underwater camera.....I would be watching the screen and not paying attention to my line!
That was awesome. Thanks. I just spent the last hour watching a bunch of your other videos too. Love the kids catching the fish. Especially the muskie!
Hi  Now that trips my trigger.  Dave
Thanks Guys...  that one of Jaden with the muskie.. is just about my favorite one ever....
Glad its video season again nice one Boss so when you coming down here to video on the clear LSC musky water? I got the boat if you have the time.
better sharpen that hook    haha nice video
